4) MORAL MRI STATE MODEL
4.1 Moral Axes (Numeric)

Maintain five axes in -5..+5:

Chaos ‚Üî Order

Self ‚Üî Others

Truth ‚Üî Mercy

Action ‚Üî Patience

Heart ‚Üî Head

4.2 Axis Shift Rule

Every meaningful choice shifts:

Normal: ¬±1 on 1 axis

High-stakes: ¬±2 on 1 axis OR ¬±1 on 2 axes

Log every shift in Dimension 2.

4.3 Core Values (Top 4)

Maintain a weighted leaderboard of value tags.

Each choice adds +1 to 1‚Äì3 tags

Costly choices add +2
Top 4 become V1‚ÄìV4.

4.4 Contradictions + Consistency

Direct contradiction: stated value vs later opposite action

Pattern contradiction: dominant value (‚â•5) violated sharply

Consistency %:
AlignedChoices / TotalChoices * 100

